| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4298 — Recovery Inhibition (play)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ea4ccf6e-fdc6-58f2-a1fa-5483987ef2fa"
